Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:02:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林  松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫罗兰\N莲藕…唉呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令尊的知交\N在这么偏僻的森林中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的好  我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从空中传来声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正想差不多\N该是你来的时候了  杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你早就知道我会来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朴仙翁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.10,0:03:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来找我是为了刀的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第51话 犬夜叉的心被吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉都告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我追琥珀的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.74,0:04:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有毒蜂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风穴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连毒蜂也吸进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你去追珊瑚还有戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜牺牲自己战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只为了我和琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:04:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你之后我也会自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了把你从奈落手里夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我而害你\N吸入了那些毒虫的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊…瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要一副那么难过的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀的事情…还有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:05:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  不要  振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点  法师…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  我打水来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒的状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想知道的事情是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲的遗物  铁碎牙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树木妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷  这东西到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,树龄两千年的朴树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且杀生丸的父亲所遗留的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙与天生牙的刀鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是用我的枝干削出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀鞘…原来那把刀的刀鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是用这家伙的枝干做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刀鞘不可思议的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到这家伙也就可想而知了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朴仙翁  你应该知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉与铁碎牙的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…你同父异母的弟弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的血已经变了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次是铁碎牙\N被鬼咬碎的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.44,0:07:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次是和我缠斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开铁碎牙的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.96,0:07:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这气味…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从半妖之血的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.97,0:08:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成和我与父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.10,0:08:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪之血的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的妖怪之血吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉是\N妖怪与人类所生的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法成为真正的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.06,0:08:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和你不同  杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯碎的妖怪的你做得到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对犬夜叉而言是却做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉做不到的事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是  保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护自己?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  好比说杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从来没有在战斗中\N被逼得走投无路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因而心灰意冷到失去自我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把我逼到走投无路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许真是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是犬夜叉不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.44,0:09:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在走投无路  生命垂危的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪之血就会支配身体而妖化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是犬夜叉从你父亲身上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继承的大妖怪之血
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对半妖的身体而言太强烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一来  会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心会被妖怪之血吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己是谁都分不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至会敌我不分的杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.91,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在不断反覆妖化中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一日犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会完全丧失理智
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后化身为只会战斗的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持续战斗至身体毁灭为止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲应该不希望\N犬夜叉变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会将当作\N护身之刀的铁碎牙交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙是护身之刀?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将它放开的时候  犬夜叉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得犬夜叉成熟多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在夸奖你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.83,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样  你救了琥珀一命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不想\N让奈落称心如意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能让琥珀活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙一定会气个半死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在说反话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为戈薇还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.96,0:11:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也有点不安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为犬夜叉一直没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口还很痛吧?让我看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  我自己治疗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好彻底治疗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是更严重怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我是想道谢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,道谢  是指什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们  戈薇  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们陪伴着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.16,0:11:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪伴着她?那是应该的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,声音从那边传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爷爷  我爷爷他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里  老头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙没有妖怪的气息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里  在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脚不小心踩空了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什~么~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:56.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为妖怪出现\N让人担心个半死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了  爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.73,0:13:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我扭到脚正不知所措呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙各位这样照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里  举手之劳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您就别放在心上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的  我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么您保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有妖怪狗哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.63,0:13:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的宝物送给你当谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他给了你什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇蜕下的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是蛇的蜕皮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好呢  犬夜叉给我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就没有时间去帮别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是举手之劳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每次做了好事之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定会变的很不爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且人数还不少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒起烟来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是刚才老头\N与小鬼的村子的方向吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们被什么袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  治疗一下小鬼的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.48,0:15:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚  你留在这里保护戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这村子我很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在食物吃完前就待在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.21,0:15:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人通通集中在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑的就杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是强盗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些小喽罗等等再收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫头目出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  强盗群中…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.04,0:15:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我闻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有只妖怪混在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子…你的刀挺有意思的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然率领着强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头目是妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼  那把刀交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?你还没睡醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别大意  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我会输吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不交出那把刀  我就用抢的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思  抢得到就来抢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉应该还无法随心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用很重的铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要扒掉你那伪装的皮  妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊!头目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头目的大钺被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活该
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是锋利的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的话就纳命来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有面盾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经中了我的毒粉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是把好刀  我愈来愈中意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头目…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.42,0:19:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我是妖怪就怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么厉害的妖怪当头目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是无敌的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会像以前一样跟随您的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿  活该
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是毒茧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不留神碰到的话会融化的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的家伙\N马上就会尸骨无存了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是毒茧  一直碰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论是谁都会溶化的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那些家伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有溶化?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从内部张开了结界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  你还能动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种烂茧我马上撕破它
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体无法动弹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才让你淋到的毒粉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经从伤口进入体内了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样一步步去见阎王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.35,0:20:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铁碎牙被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头目请
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被铁碎牙的结界拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头目?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么刀会拒绝我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的铁碎牙会选择主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说像你这种杂碎妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不配持有它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是这些\N杂碎般的人类强盗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被刀选上的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说杂碎太狠了吧  头目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.40,0:21:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  你这小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个半妖对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是太滑稽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个区区的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.38,0:21:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢向我妖怪蛾天丸找碴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了  一定是在村子出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好担心爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不但没有好  反而愈来愈大了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  血止不住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.41,0:22:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是毒粉的关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是张开结界就很勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.75,0:22:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法活动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.42,0:22:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这结界能撑到什么时候呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.96,0:22:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  头目  这把刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.99,0:22:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你处置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.73,0:22:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对不能用的刀没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢头目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把刀无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非交给那个人不可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这把刀真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.25,0:22:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结界破掉  被毒茧融化\N是迟早的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在这里等着看好戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把女孩带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:49.66,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.00,0:24:01.14,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:08.58,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:12.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:17.06,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:24.06,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,便能看见 你的笑容{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:31.27,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah- 但愿从此以往
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.11,0:24:38.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,直到进入 沉眠的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.58,0:24:46.32,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 那抹笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.99,0:24:54.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,都绝没有 消逝的瞬间{\fad(0,900)}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.89,0:25:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被毒蛾妖怪蛾天丸\N困在毒茧中的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.72,0:25:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到凶猛的妖怪之血支配
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.96,0:25:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫不留情的杀光强盗们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.00,0:25:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样才能解除犬夜叉的妖化呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.87,0:25:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师  珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.27,0:25:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快想个让他恢复原状的办法
